          "name": "How does Cambridge Enterprise support new ventures?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "They support new ventures by providing seed funding, expert mentorship, intellectual property protection, and access to a vast network of industry partners and investors."
